Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\OneDrive
and change DWORD strings
DisableFileSyncNGSC
DisableLocation
DisableLibrariesDefaultSaveToOneDrive
DisableFileSync
to
1

and DWORD string
DisableMeteredNetworkFileSync
to
0

&

Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\ControlSet001\Control\Storage\EnabledDenyGP
and change DWORD string
DenyAllGPState
to
1


Finish.
